There is time until January 4th, 2010 to send in your video pitch for your
cause if you want a chance to participate in the [World economic Forum at
Davos](http://www.weforum.org/en/events/AnnualMeeting2010/index.htm) in
Switzerland. Read all instructions and Conditions to participate on the [Davos
YouTube Channel](http://www.youtube.com/user/thedavosquestion) or [on their
site](http://www.weforum.org/pdf/AMNC09/AMNC09_DavosDebatesSubmissionGuidelines.pdf).

